{"tid":1115553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估地方) 人妻講電話遭揉乳10分鐘　「我不是妓女」怒提告","createTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T19:25:04.000Z","uid":224860,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"acbc653cd4871802e1ade4ed96e7e18507a4ce1c","tid":1115553,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"一名有3個小孩的人妻，穿短袖時講手機，男子手就從袖子下方空隙伸進去揉奶捏乳頭，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時間長達5到10分鐘，讓人妻怒提告</span></span></span></strong>，台中地院依強制猥褻罪，處有期徒刑10個月。<br />\n<br />\n台中地院判決書指出，38歲人妻阿嬌(化名)，在2017年2月18日下午帶著小孩在街上時，遇到朋友阿明(化名)，雙方就一起到一江橋旁聊天，之後阿嬌去接兒子放學，阿明就邀阿嬌跟她小孩到他的住處參觀，到了晚上時，阿明趁阿嬌用手機跟友人通話時，將手伸進阿嬌衣袖下擺，再伸入至阿嬌胸罩內撫摸、揉捏胸部、乳頭，雖阿嬌推及閃避，阿明不顧反對續撫摸、揉捏，阿嬌遂帶子女離開且報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌指出，他當時到阿明的租屋處，她坐在床的外圍，開始要講電話，阿明趁她講電話的時候，用他的右手從她衣服下擺伸進內衣裡摸胸，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過程約5到10分鐘</span></strong>，掛掉電話後用力推阿明說：「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你怎麼可以這樣摸我，我不是妓女</span></strong>。」<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而阿嬌的兒子也說「</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我在阿明的家中看到阿明一直摸媽媽的胸部，當時媽媽是在講電話</strong></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n阿明辯稱，是阿嬌拿他的電話聊天，要她將電話歸還，拿電話時摸到她的胸部，但之後又說：「我沒有摸阿嬌的胸部，我只有推她的肩頭」，到了審理時改辯稱：「可能有碰觸阿嬌，但沒有伸進去摸胸部」。<br />\n<br />\n地院認為被告所辯前後不一，審理過程中數次無正當理由不到庭，且未與阿嬌和解或賠償，可見其毫無悔意，犯後態度顯然不佳，依強制猥褻罪，處有期徒刑10個月。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190419/1553425/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190419%2F1553425%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=1bef8920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190419%2F1553425%2F&h=c08f65c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190419/1553425/</a>"},{"pid":"05cb9aa9f31b3461866f0fbf118aabe8d7bb20e3","tid":1115553,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"咩劇情黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69669aca860ce474c1748a1b833825e26bb782a","tid":1115553,"uid":4559,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afcb01d9c5377cf800063ab523f6069aba979b40","tid":1115553,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"淨係揸波，蝕咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b1120b5e9c40d61e129887b627b469e7331a84","tid":1115553,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b92f636dbe3522ec7aea634c721c23a9bcd5c52","tid":1115553,"uid":48702,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"隻雞去到個sp屋企坐埋上床再俾人揸波揸10分鐘<br />\n應該係講完個電話準備扑野但唔小心俾個細路撞破先發難"},{"pid":"61625d5b035d70ad3564b028af9b47beabe7ffbc","tid":1115553,"uid":48702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"個臭系可能唔係雞，係淫系搵sp姐"},{"pid":"59bdbe5cbf60f918ca118aea48432fb6b7d6af1d","tid":1115553,"uid":231293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"我不是妓女<br />\n<br />\n我不要錢<br />\n<br />\n我要大肉棒!"},{"pid":"734596cbd8c20904ac5aa70f42a875366d0813bb","tid":1115553,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQyJ5d7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQyJ5d7.gif&h=f3277444&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4119663db9f32b01cc35079478d091c3cb72954e","tid":1115553,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:15:55.000Z","msg